title: Large 2 bedroom in Lynn now Available
posting_body: ['Large 2 bedroom 1 Bath apartment in the Historical Diamond district of Lynn is now available.', 'NO BROKER FEE', '●10 ft. high ceilings throughout.', '● Beautiful old-world charm hardwood floors in the Livingroom, bedroom and foyer.', '● Less than a 5-minute walk to the beach, Central Square Station, bus line 441/442 and Commuter Rail.', '5-minute drive to Market Basket and other Grocery stores.', '● Experience the wonders of old town, Union Street for shopping and dining.', '● Ample street parking with permit.', '● Heat and hot water included.', '● Gas range', '● Very quiet corner unit on the 2th floor.', '● Onsite Property Manager.', '● Laundry room in the building.', '● Elevator in the building', "First and last month's rent due at signing", '$750.00 Security Deposit.', 'Must have verifiable income and able to pass a background check.', 'Private viewing available by contacting the General Manager']
